text: Hillsboro is a city in Ohio, United States. It is the county seat of Highland County. 6,481 people lived in Hillsboro, according to information from the 2020 census. The plan of Hillsboro was mapped in 1807, and most likely named for the hills near the original town site. == References == Category:Cities in Ohio Category:County seats in Ohio
title: Hillsboro, Ohio
